# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisasurface2.rpy:13
translate chinese lisasurface2_1c1d5032:

    # pc "Do you like to drink? Alcohol, I mean? I don't think I've ever seen you drink."
    pc "你喜欢喝酒吗？我是说酒精饮料？我好像从来没见过你喝酒。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisasurface2.rpy:15
translate chinese lisasurface2_1d3bb110:

    # sp "I don't drink a lot, but I'll occasionally have a glass of wine."
    sp "我不怎么喝，但偶尔会喝一杯红酒。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisasurface2.rpy:16
translate chinese lisasurface2_c72b71ab:

    # pc "No beer or shots?"
    pc "不喝啤酒或烈酒？"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisasurface2.rpy:17
translate chinese lisasurface2_53d5d4b7:

    # sp "I'm not a big fan of the taste of most beers and shots get me drunk way too fast."
    sp "我不太喜欢大多数啤酒的味道，而且烈酒让我醉得太快了。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisasurface2.rpy:18
translate chinese lisasurface2_d27b8712:

    # sp "I'm kind of a light weight. One or two shots and I'm out of it."
    sp "我酒量不太好。喝一两杯我就晕乎乎的。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisasurface2.rpy:20
translate chinese lisasurface2_4ee2ab04:

    # sp "And when I get drunk I get, super handsy."
    sp "而且我一喝醉，手就特别不老实。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisasurface2.rpy:21
translate chinese lisasurface2_85be51df:

    # sp "Got me in trouble a bit back in my college days."
    sp "大学那会儿还因此惹过点麻烦。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisasurface2.rpy:22
translate chinese lisasurface2_ae871f39:

    # pc "Oh yeah?"
    pc "哦，是吗？"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisasurface2.rpy:23
translate chinese lisasurface2_11f2ea04:

    # sp "Yeah. How do you think Suzy happened?"
    sp "是啊。你以为苏茜是怎么来的？"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisasurface2.rpy:24
translate chinese lisasurface2_285ddc7d:

    # pc "Oh no!"
    pc "哦不！"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisasurface2.rpy:26
translate chinese lisasurface2_1b76ce0b:

    # sp "No way I would have ever hooked up with her dad if I hadn't had a few shots."
    sp "要不是喝了几杯烈酒，我绝对不可能跟她老爸发生关系。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisasurface2.rpy:27
translate chinese lisasurface2_7c919ce5:

    # sp "It turned out pretty good though. I got a great daughter out of it."
    sp "不过结果还挺好的。我因此有了个可爱的女儿。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisasurface2.rpy:29
translate chinese lisasurface2_a61b3105:

    # sp "But no more shots for me. They just lead to mistakes."
    sp "但我再也不喝烈酒了。它们只会让人犯错。"

